# TrustLens AI — Progress Report
**Date:** March 9, 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Project:** AI-Powered Product Condition Verification Platform

---

## 1. Project Overview

TrustLens AI is a full-stack web application that allows users to upload product images and receive a comprehensive AI-powered condition verification report — including damage detection, severity scoring, price recommendation, and a human-readable explanation.

**Use case:** Enabling transparent, trust-based transactions in the second-hand/refurbished product marketplace by providing objective, AI-driven product condition assessments.

